{"id": 58378, "date": "2025-08-15T04:00:16", "date_gmt": "2025-08-15T11:00:16", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=58378"}, "modified": "2026-06-18T04:56:19", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-18T11:56:19", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-15-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/15/kingdom-of-days-august-15-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 15"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1969:\u00a0</strong>Child plays a gig at the Student Prince in Asbury Park.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>On Night Three of Bruce&#8217;s legendary stand at New York City&#8217;s Bottom Line, the early show is broadcast live on WNEW-FM, resulting in one of Bruce&#8217;s most widely bootlegged shows ever. Listen to that historic broadcast below.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLmxwNSnqgfedcTVTpET4evBCavu-lOISm\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>There&#8217;s no audio from the late show, and that&#8217;s too bad: it features the last known performance of &#8220;New York City Serenade&#8221; for 24 years.</p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds a recording session for his upcoming album at Atlantic Studios in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band deliver a scorching performance at Washington DC&#8217;s Capital Center (actually in Largo, Maryland)&#8211;and we know just how good it was because we can see for ourselves: this show is captured in stunning quality (for the time). Watch below to see the E Street Band at the height of their powers.</p>\n<div id=\"v-YnjIaFFn-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/YnjIaFFn?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-j6U6TOXs-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/j6U6TOXs?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Cats on a Smooth Surface at their fourth anniversary party at The Stone Pony. Amazingly, the set was captured on film&#8211;check out &#8220;Jersey Girl&#8221; and &#8220;Sweet Soul Music&#8221; below.</p>\n<div id=\"v-5WvffBvQ-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/5WvffBvQ?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two nights at Philadelphia&#8217;s Veterans Stadium on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/m8p5z71YIrY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDm8p5z71YIrY\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20400\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-08-15a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15a.png?fit=1451%2C1641&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1451,1641\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-08-15a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15a.png?fit=758%2C858&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20400 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15a.png?resize=758%2C857&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"857\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15a.png?w=1451&amp;ssl=1 1451w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15a.png?resize=265%2C300&amp;ssl=1 265w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15a.png?resize=905%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 905w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15a.png?resize=768%2C869&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15a.png?resize=1358%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1358w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20401\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-08-15b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15b.png?fit=2071%2C1109&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2071,1109\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-08-15b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15b.png?fit=758%2C406&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20401 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15b.png?resize=758%2C406&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"406\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15b.png?w=2071&amp;ssl=1 2071w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15b.png?resize=300%2C161&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15b.png?resize=1024%2C548&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15b.png?resize=768%2C411&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15b.png?resize=1536%2C823&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-15b.png?resize=2048%2C1097&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce brings the Rising Tour to Detroit for one night at The Palace of Auburn Hills, where the set list remains unchanged for the fourth consecutive show&#8211;but that&#8217;s about to change.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zAlYkHYg8qYNezIwJuhOkB3\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20402\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2002-08-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-15-e1781783752940.png?fit=2078%2C679&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2078,679\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2002-08-15\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-15-e1781783752940.png?fit=758%2C248&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20402 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-15-e1781783752940.png?resize=758%2C248&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"248\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-15-e1781783752940.png?w=2078&amp;ssl=1 2078w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-15-e1781783752940.png?resize=300%2C98&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-15-e1781783752940.png?resize=1024%2C335&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-15-e1781783752940.png?resize=768%2C251&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-15-e1781783752940.png?resize=1536%2C502&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-15-e1781783752940.png?resize=2048%2C669&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2008:\u00a0</strong>The Magic Tour enters its final month with a return to indoor arenas, starting with this show in Jacksonville. Bruce tour premieres &#8220;You Can&#8217;t Sit Down,&#8221; played for the first time in almost a decade, as well as &#8220;Back in Your Arms.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-oc0WivO0-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/oc0WivO0?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/c7R8BLSvYEQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Night Two at Boston&#8217;s Fenway Park brings an embarrassment of riches, from an opening &#8220;Thunder Road&#8221; with just Bruce and Roy, to an almost completely audibled opening pack, to the first &#8220;Knock on Wood&#8221; in 36 years, to the first &#8220;Prove It &#8217;78&#8221; in the U.S.A. since &#8217;78, a guest-spot by Ken Casey, and so much more. This show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div id=\"v-FaVCWMDK-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/FaVCWMDK?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-b3Y5W7XT-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/b3Y5W7XT?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/z3u8-LpUISk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"VideoPress Video Player\" aria-label=\"VideoPress Video Player\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://videopress.com/embed/zkaKIjie?hd=0&amp;cover=1\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"clipboard-write\"></iframe><script src='https://v0.wordpress.com/js/next/videopress-iframe.js?m=1770107250'></script></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/n8kIjzIZL5g?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xkYYNPzRljs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oCixUwho8mw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City. In attendance tonight: Gloria Steinem.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"12133\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/gloriasteinem/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/gloriasteinem.jpg?fit=500%2C493&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"500,493\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1534425823&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0